{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-contents-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/contents/15th-algorithm-study-memoir/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"자바에서-벗어나자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EB%B2%97%EC%96%B4%EB%82%98%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"자바에서 벗어나자 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>자바에서 벗어나자!</h1>\n<p>알고리즘 문제를 해결하는데 있어 스터디 처음부터 지속적으로 Java 를 사용해왔다.</p>\n<p>이유는 추 후 자바 백엔드 취업을 지향하고 있으며, 자바언어로 코테를 보는 회사가 많았기 때문에</p>\n<p>선행 연습 겸 사용해왔던 건데, 현a역 군인인 나에게 대학교 2년도 남았는데 너무 먼 미래같기도 하고,</p>\n<p>자바로 문제 푸는 행위 자체가 지루해졌다.</p>\n<p>진짜 이젠 이런게 제일 싫었다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"java\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">    System.out.println(&quot;x: &quot; + x + &quot;y : &quot; + y);</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>여러 값을 직관적으로 눈디버깅하기 위해 콘솔을 찍는 행위..\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/eea4a/sisidie.jpg' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 56.19047619047619%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='시시해서죽고싶어졌다.jpg' title='시시해서죽고싶어졌다.jpg' src='/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/65f94/sisidie.jpg' srcset='/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/d2682/sisidie.jpg 105w,\n/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/60342/sisidie.jpg 210w,\n/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/65f94/sisidie.jpg 420w,\n/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/828fb/sisidie.jpg 630w,\n/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/bba1f/sisidie.jpg 840w,\n/static/b787b8a9e4feefff52339a3cf0869652/eea4a/sisidie.jpg 1280w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그래서 java 와 호환되는 코틀린도 살짝 맛보고 이번 주차 스터디 진행은 c++ 로 진행해봤다.</p>\n<p>다른 언어들만큼 c++ 이 콘솔찍는 행위가 편한건 아니긴한데 java 보다 낫다.</p>\n<p>오랜만에 빠른 언어도 써보고싶었기도 하다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"해결한-문제-회고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"해결한 문제 회고 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결한 문제 회고</h1>\n<h3 id=\"백준-쇠막대기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B1%EC%A4%80-%EC%87%A0%EB%A7%89%EB%8C%80%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"백준 쇠막대기 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[백준] 쇠막대기</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.acmicpc.net/problem/107990\">10799. 쇠막대기</a>\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='막대기문제.png' title='막대기문제.png' src='/static/2b264efff2ad92a12ad3ebcb9acf6ba7/d10fb/pipe.png' srcset='/static/2b264efff2ad92a12ad3ebcb9acf6ba7/79c17/pipe.png 105w,\n/static/2b264efff2ad92a12ad3ebcb9acf6ba7/65ed1/pipe.png 210w,\n/static/2b264efff2ad92a12ad3ebcb9acf6ba7/d10fb/pipe.png 420w,\n/static/2b264efff2ad92a12ad3ebcb9acf6ba7/a07a7/pipe.png 534w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n    </span></p>\n<p>() 를 레이저로 취급하여 총 몇 개의 파이프가 절단되었는 지 갯수를 세는 스택 문제이다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\r\n#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\r\n#include &lt;stack&gt;\r\n\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nint main() {\r\n  ios::sync_with_stdio(false);\r\n  cin.tie(nullptr);\r\n\r\n  stack&lt;char&gt; S;\r\n  string input;\r\n  int total = 0;\r\n  cin &gt;&gt; input;\r\n  for (int i = 0; i &lt; input.length(); i++) {\r\n    if (input[i] == &#39;(&#39;) {\r\n      S.push(input[i]);\r\n    } else if (input[i] == &#39;)&#39; &amp;&amp; input[i - 1] == &#39;(&#39;) {\r\n      S.pop();\r\n      total += S.size();\r\n    } else {\r\n      S.pop();\r\n      total++;\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  cout &lt;&lt; total &lt;&lt; endl;\r\n}</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>입력 값 string 을 순회 돌려서</p>\n<p>'(' 일 시 stack 에 넣고</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">    if (input[i] == &#39;(&#39;) {\r\n      S.push(input[i]);\r\n    }</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>'()' 인 경우를 판단해 stack 의 사이즈 만큼 더하고</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">else if (input[i] == &#39;)&#39; &amp;&amp; input[i - 1] == &#39;(&#39;) {\r\n      S.pop();\r\n      total += S.size();\r\n    } </code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>')' 일 경우 파이프를 자르면 한 개가 더 남는 원리로 +1 을 수행한다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">else {\r\n      S.pop();\r\n      total++;\r\n    }</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"leetcode-reverse-linked-list\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#leetcode-reverse-linked-list\" aria-label=\"leetcode reverse linked list permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[LeetCode] Reverse Linked List</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/reverse-linked-list/\">206. Reverse Linked List</a>\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 40.952380952380956%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='rere.jpg' title='rere.jpg' src='/static/49f3322c7abc9a0c7cf637264e677bc2/65f94/rev1ex1.jpg' srcset='/static/49f3322c7abc9a0c7cf637264e677bc2/d2682/rev1ex1.jpg 105w,\n/static/49f3322c7abc9a0c7cf637264e677bc2/60342/rev1ex1.jpg 210w,\n/static/49f3322c7abc9a0c7cf637264e677bc2/65f94/rev1ex1.jpg 420w,\n/static/49f3322c7abc9a0c7cf637264e677bc2/a34d8/rev1ex1.jpg 542w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이 문제는 저번에도 풀었던 건데 늘 어떻게 풀었는 지 원리를 생각하면 잘 생각이 안난다..\r\n참조를 왔다갔다 하는 구조가 늘 머리에 안익는다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"c\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"material\" line-numbers=\"true\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\r\n#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\r\n#include &lt;stack&gt;\r\n\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nstruct ListNode {\r\n  int val;\r\n  ListNode *next;\r\n  ListNode() : val(0), next(nullptr) {}\r\n  ListNode(int x) : val(x), next(nullptr) {}\r\n  ListNode(int x, ListNode *next) : val(x), next(next) {}\r\n};\r\n\r\nclass Solution {\r\npublic:\r\n  ListNode* reverseList(ListNode* head) {\r\n    ListNode *nextNode, *prevNode = nullptr;\r\n    while (head) {\r\n      nextNode = head-&gt;next;\r\n      head-&gt;next = prevNode;\r\n      prevNode = head;\r\n      head = nextNode;\r\n    }\r\n    return prevNode;\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n}</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"그-외-풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8-%EC%99%B8-%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"그 외 풀이 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그 외 풀이</h3>\n<p>코틀린 맛보기 겸 코틀린으로 쉬운 문제 몇 개와 SQL을 하도 안쓰니 기억이 잘 안나서\r\n프로그래머스에서 쉬운 문제 몇 개를 풀었다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"마감하며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EA%B0%90%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"마감하며 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마감하며</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.banksalad.com/tech/build-a-website-with-gatsby/\">Gatsby.js</a> 를 공부하고 블로그 기능들을 작성하는데 재미 들렸다.</p>\n<p>graphql 이 너무 생소하고 처음엔 <a href=\"https://blog.banksalad.com/tech/build-a-website-with-gatsby/\">Gatsby.js</a> 의 구조가 너무 어려워서 어지러웠지만</p>\n<p>지금은 어느정도 적응한 듯 하다. 빨리 TOL 기능도 만들고 아직 맘에들지 않은 디자인을 어떻게 개선할\r\n지 고민도 해야한다.</p>\n<p>잠시 중단되었던 홈쇼핑 프로젝트도 재개해야하니 늘 바쁜 생각 속에 살아간다.</p>\n<p>오늘도 실천하자.\r\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 420px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/6e9ba/1028_me.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='내현황' title='내현황' src='/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/d10fb/1028_me.png' srcset='/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/79c17/1028_me.png 105w,\n/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/65ed1/1028_me.png 210w,\n/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/d10fb/1028_me.png 420w,\n/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/f058b/1028_me.png 630w,\n/static/319a2672bba5d0fbde1b22f905877c4d/6e9ba/1028_me.png 731w' sizes='(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://alg-study-helper-chi.vercel.app/\">알고리즘 스터디 웹 서비스</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.banksalad.com/tech/build-a-website-with-gatsby/\">React밖에 모르는 당신에게. GatsbyJS한 잔, '채용~'</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9E%90%EB%B0%94%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EB%B2%97%EC%96%B4%EB%82%98%EC%9E%90\">자바에서 벗어나자!</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%9A%8C%EA%B3%A0\">해결한 문제 회고</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B1%EC%A4%80-%EC%87%A0%EB%A7%89%EB%8C%80%EA%B8%B0\">[백준] 쇠막대기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#leetcode-reverse-linked-list\">[LeetCode] Reverse Linked List</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8-%EC%99%B8-%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\">그 외 풀이</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EA%B0%90%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0\">마감하며</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"10월 4주차 알고리즘 스터디 회고록","date":"2022년 10월 28일","slug":"15th-algorithm-study-memoir","tag":["Algorithm"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"3d2f6569-2dae-517e-960a-26cec241391e","frontmatter__slug":"15th-algorithm-study-memoir","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"15th-algorithm-study-memoir"}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}